data.text:
Textures for VirtualCol Airbus A220-300 model. Compatibility: FSX, P3D

It is presented to your attention 4 external of world-known airlines textures of ultra high resolution (4096 px) for the VirtualCol Airbus A220-300 model on a completely new and completely redesigned paintkit.

1. American Airlines - New Colors

2. United Airlines - New Colors

3. Lufthansa - New Colors

4. S7 Airlines - New Colors

A brand new paint set was created in the highest resolution. The textures of the fuselage, engines, wings and other external parts of the aircraft were repainted, as well as all other details of the external textures of the aircraft.

At the same time specular and bump textures were also re-drawn. You can look at my screenshots by comparing my and original textures and see the differences.

All textures have a resolution of 4096 pixels. This is 2 times more compared to the original textures.

All my changes are presented in the screenshots. Now you can enjoy flying, making flights on ultra high definition livery :)

NOTES:

There was no significant decrease in FPS due to 4K textures.
